sequenceDiagram
    participant A as 发送者前端
    participant WS as ChatWebSocket
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant C as ChatMessageConsumer
    participant MG as MongoDB
    participant B as 接收者前端

    A->>A: 乐观更新：本地显示消息(status=sending)
    A->>WS: wsSend({type:"text", content})
    WS->>MQ: chatMessageProducer.sendChatMessage()
    MQ->>C: 消费消息
    C->>C: 检查接收者在线 → true
    C->>MG: 保存消息(status=sending)
    C->>MQ: 发送延迟ACK超时消息(30s)
    C->>WS: broadcastToConversation()
    WS->>A: {type:"message", data} (替换临时消息)
    WS->>B: {type:"message", data}
    B->>WS: wsSend({type:"ack", messageId})
    WS->>MG: updateMessageStatus("sent")
    WS->>A: {type:"ack", messageId}
    A->>A: status = "sent"，转圈消失
